&lt;td class="content"&gt;
This article has no meaningful content. Instead, I use it to make sure everything works before working out "the real stuff".
&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;/table&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class="sect1"&gt;
&lt;h2 id="_the_idea"&gt;The Idea&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class="sectionbody"&gt;
&lt;div class="paragraph"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Hello, world is the canonical example of an application that does a minimalist thing. It is used mostly to make sure that the toolchain is operational - code should be compiled, linked and executed.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class="paragraph"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;In that manner, this post is my "Hello, World!" - I want to test that the whole blog infrastructure is working.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class="sect1"&gt;
&lt;h2 id="_source_code"&gt;Source Code&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class="sectionbody"&gt;
&lt;div class="listingblock"&gt;
&lt;div class="title"&gt;Hello, world in Java&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class="content"&gt;
&lt;pre class="pygments highlight"&gt;&lt;code data-lang="java"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="tok-kd"&gt;public&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="tok-kd"&gt;class&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="tok-nc"&gt;HelloWorld&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="tok-o"&gt;{&lt;/span&gt;
	&lt;span class="tok-cm"&gt;/**&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class="tok-cm"&gt;	 * Comment goes here&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class="tok-cm"&gt;	 **/&lt;/span&gt;
	&lt;span class="tok-kd"&gt;public&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="tok-kd"&gt;static&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="tok-kd"&gt;final&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="tok-kt"&gt;void&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="tok-nf"&gt;main&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="tok-o"&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="tok-n"&gt;String&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="tok-o"&gt;[]&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="tok-n"&gt;args&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="tok-o"&gt;)&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="tok-o"&gt;{&lt;/span&gt;
		&lt;span class="tok-n"&gt;System&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="tok-o"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="tok-na"&gt;out&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="tok-o"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="tok-na"&gt;println&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="tok-o"&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="tok-s"&gt;&amp;quot;Hello, World!&amp;quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="tok-o"&gt;);&lt;/span&gt; &lt;i class="conum" data-value="1"&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;b&gt;(1)&lt;/b&gt;
